,"uid":6030,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:14:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7NGpV1d.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7NGpV1d.gif&h=d624c6ac&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:35:30.000Z","msg":"全盛時期<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"451d6fffaf8724d1adb082c01efae615e8e257f9","tid":1776323,"uid":34489,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:47:28.000Z","msg":"我願意出錢幫佢隆胸‧‧‧"},{"pid":"93a98f8c643982f69eec0a5e775d14378403ea42","tid":1776323,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:47:56.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">尋找黑警性暴力證人/受害者，協助國際遊說</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2640629789347426&amp;id=124616407615456\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2640629789347426%26id%3D124616407615456&d=qnVsOlgekcepRBzFpIlw%2F1YPZSwMlx1ag7qd%2FaAfmLs%3D&h=2c3f73b9\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2640629789347426&amp;id=124616407615456</a><br />\n<br />\nPost：<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eDEkrT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eDEkrT</a><br />\n<br />\n//平等機會婦女聯席發言人區美寶稱，3個組織11月初共同發起控訴警察性暴力的國際聯署，截至本月7日收集到21國共85個團體聯署支持。為了向聯合國專家展開更有力游說，3個組織呼籲受害者主動聯絡他們並接受訪談，強調會保密。//<br />\n<br />\n我們現正收集抗爭者在抗爭期間／被捕後遭受警察性暴力對待的資料，作以下用途：<br />\n1. 協助受害人可以完整保留該事件之紀錄<br />\n2. 整理資料並製成 #ProtestToo 實錄，以作追究之用<br />\n3. 收集國際聯署（進行中），結合個案提交聯合國，爭取國際間關注及支持<br />\n4. 要求香港政府獨立、公正地徹查「反送中運動」發生的性暴力<br />\n<br />\n*個人資料及通訊紀錄在實錄完成後可按受訪者意願全部銷毀<br />\n詳情及相關安排請聯絡Tg @protesttoo"},{"pid":"52effe68f5821e8848e530ea80b0c28e1fb16956","tid":1776323,"uid":25857,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"97cded3cd556e6b02a4c9e73639d4295920cd1ce","tid":1776323,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a70d854ad1d839b1e82ebf7d9f9025656e706df9","tid":1776323,"uid":25857,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:03:24.000Z","msg":"又真係幾靚"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:05:50.000Z","msg":"真係超靚，完美女神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:48:33.000Z","msg":"個樣可以彌補無波呢個缺點"},{"pid":"0349d04b7150bc33de0ad695c5586cc0d9ff57a7","tid":1776323,"uid":76098,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:50:26.000Z","msg":"heidi有波可以統治世界"},{"pid":"b7c6b7f54464cfe71e76f20020b2b45cdafca3a8","tid":1776323,"uid":127553,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:50:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UmKV2z6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUmKV2z6.jpg&h=241aee25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有班教育界痴線佬為左唔比學生落入聖誕節圈套<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1776399\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1776399</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n昨日遊行最深刻的一句「初夏&mdash;&mdash;寒冬」<br />\n我們不經不覺由初夏走到冬天<br />\n由撐黃色食店走到黃色經濟圈<br />\n香港人就是有心有力也有財力<br />\n<br />\n講返正題，以往每年聖誕聯歡/Re-U都總係會叫啲最方便快捷嘅KFC、PizzaHut聖誕套餐，今年相信大家都不了不了，所以我地整合左所有會做到會服務嘅黃店，大家識Do啦！<br />\n*（亦建議學生會將圖印出派比同學宣傳📃）<br />\n<br />\n最後，教育同行全體祝大家有個Yellow Christmas 🎄💛<br />\n<br />\n*我地已盡量向店方直接確認到會服務，但始終人手有限，資料未必齊全，歡迎各位Comment報料。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nTg: <a href=\"https://t.me/hkteacher\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkteacher&d=qnVsOlgekcepRBzFpIlw%2F1YPZSwMlx1ag7qd%2FaAfmLs%3D&h=a33451d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkteacher</a><br />\nFb: shorturl.at/kqtJM<br />\nIg: <a href=\"https://instagram.com/standbyeducatorshk?igshid=juzv8s7rtxb5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fstandbyeducatorshk%3Figshid%3Djuzv8s7rtxb5&d=qnVsOlgekcepRBzFpIlw%2F1YPZSwMlx1ag7qd%2FaAfmLs%3D&h=58cf8c0e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/standbyeducatorshk?igshid